      "Text": "Security update for ncurses",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for ncurses fixes the following issue:\n\n- CVE-2025-69720: buffer overflow in function `analyze_string()`of `progs/infocmp.c` (bsc#1259924).\n",
